Package: MDTToolset
Title: Detection of Most Dominant Transcripts (MDTs), MDT Switches and their Functional Impacts
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tulay", "Karakulak", , "tulaykarakulak@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This tool is designed to detect the most dominant transcripts, their switches between two different conditions, and their functional impact on protein interaction network.
